## 📊 Migration Guide

### v0.5.16 → v0.5.17

1. **Update test dependencies**
   ```bash
   cd /opt/aitbc
   git pull
   ./venv/bin/pip install -e ".[test]"
   ```

2. **Run new tests**
   ```bash
   ./venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/unit -q
   ./venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/integration -q
   ./venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/multi_chain -q  # new
   ./venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/bridge -q       # new
   ```

