### Updated Dependencies
- Blockchain node v0.5.16+ (the fixes being tested)

## 🔐 Security Considerations

- Test fixtures must not use real keys or real blockchain state
- Test databases must be in-memory or isolated (no cross-test contamination)
- Byzantine node simulation must not leak into production networks

## 📈 Performance Targets

- Multi-chain fixture startup: <5 seconds (in-memory DBs)
- Multi-node harness startup (3 nodes): <10 seconds
- Full test suite runtime: <60 seconds (with parallel execution)
- Bridge test suite: <10 seconds

